129
00:09:16,534 --> 00:09:21,237
because of the fact that I've had the flexibility to work remotely.

130
00:09:21,717 --> 00:09:27,140
And I don't think it's as much convincing people that working remotely is great.

131
00:09:27,220 --> 00:09:29,682
I think it's a matter of convincing companies.

132
00:09:30,402 --> 00:09:35,327
That it's really to your interest to allow this as a choice for people who need it.

133
00:09:35,727 --> 00:09:37,589
Working remotely is not for everybody,

134
00:09:38,130 --> 00:09:41,833
but it is something that I think would make things better

135
00:09:42,113 --> 00:09:47,759
and help bring in a more diverse group of developers across the board

136
00:09:48,039 --> 00:09:53,484
if companies gave that choice more readily to people who would like it.

